  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, when another creature that you can see within 60 feet of you hits with a weapon attack, you can use your reaction to increase the attack's velocity, causing the attack's target to take an extra [[/r 1d10]] damage of the weapon's type.</p><p>Alternatively, if a creature within 60 feet of you takes damage from a fall, you can use your reaction to increase the fall's damage by [[/r 2d10]].</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (a minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
